{"surahDetails":{"id":102,"arabicName":"التكاثر","banglaName":"প্রাচুর্যের প্রতিযোগিতা","englishName":"Competition","enTranslatedName":"At-Takathur","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","totalWords":28,"totalLetters":122,"audio":"http://download.quranicaudio.com/quran/ahmed_ibn_3ali_al-3ajamy/102.mp3","totalAyah":8},"surah":{"id":102,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"أَلۡهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","bangl_text":"প্রাচুর্যের লালসা তোমাদেরকে গাফেল রাখে","english_text":"Competition in [worldly] increase diverts you","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/102001.mp3"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"حَتَّىٰ زُرۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَقَابِرَ","bangl_text":"এমনকি, তোমরা কবরস্থানে পৌছে যাও।","english_text":"Until you visit the graveyards","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/102002.mp3"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","bangl_text":"এটা কখনও উচিত নয়। তোমরা সত্ত্বরই জেনে নেবে।","english_text":"No! You are going to know","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/102003.mp3"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","bangl_text":"অতঃপর এটা কখনও উচিত নয়। তোমরা সত্ত্বরই জেনে নেবে।","english_text":"Then no! You are going to know","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/102004.mp3"},{"id":5,"arabic_text":"كَلَّا لَوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عِلۡمَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","bangl_text":"কখনই নয়; যদি তোমরা নিশ্চিত জানতে।","english_text":"No! If you only knew with knowledge of certainty","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/102005.mp3"},{"id":6,"arabic_text":"لَتَرَوُنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ","bangl_text":"তোমরা অবশ্যই জাহান্নাম দেখবে","english_text":"You will surely see the Hellfire","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/102006.mp3"},{"id":7,"arabic_text":"ثُمَّ لَتَرَوُنَّهَا عَيۡنَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","bangl_text":"অতঃপর তোমরা তা অবশ্যই দেখবে দিব্য প্রত্যয়ে","english_text":"Then you will surely see it with the eye of certainty","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/102007.mp3"},{"id":8,"arabic_text":"ثُمَّ لَتُسۡـَٔلُنَّ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَنِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","bangl_text":"এরপর অবশ্যই সেদিন তোমরা নেয়ামত সম্পর্কে জিজ্ঞাসিত হবে।","english_text":"Then you will surely be asked that Day about pleasure","page":600,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/102008.mp3"}]}}